'''Billy Linneman''' was shot during an insurgent attack in Iraq.

==History==
Billy was shot in an insurgent attack in Iraq. He was bandaged up in the tent and then was put on the APC to be moved to the green zone. However, on the way, they hit an IED and he died in the explosion.

==Career==
He was in the US Army.
